this xsl transforms an MDB xml schema to an old school config.xml (from BXCMS OG)

HOW-TO
======

- call reverse_engineer_xml_schema.php somewhere in your webbrowser
- fill in the appropriate values
- xsltproc mdbschema2forms.xsl /path/to/mdbschema.xml
- php5 configsinstall.php moves the configs in single dirs..

you should have now an old school forms schema config.xml for all your tables.